<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Sat, 18 Jul 2026 03:19:53 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title>小径终现地图上</title><link>https://some.pics/6a5af0cbe0b58</link><description>&lt;p&gt;很久以前我第一次跑这条路的时候可能还没有这条小路，但我发誓现在肯定有了，也许不是此刻就能看到，但你可以在地图上找到它了。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A narrow, grassy path winds through a dense, sun-dappled green forest." height="4284" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/ericmwalk/6a5af0cbe0b58.jpg" width="5712"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://ericmwalk.some.pics"&gt;@ericmwalk&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Jul 2026 03:19:53 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>老爸式幽默T恤</title><link>https://some.pics/6a5a8c9f70023</link><description>&lt;p&gt;"嗨，饿了吧，我是爸爸"T恤&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A purple T-shirt with the words &amp;quot;Hi Hungry, I'm Dad&amp;quot; embroidered in blue thread down the center." height="3072" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/ballpointcarrot/6a5a8c9f70023.jpg" width="4096"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://ballpointcarrot.some.pics"&gt;@ballpointcarrot&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Jul 2026 20:12:19 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>上下对比</title><link>https://some.pics/6a5a6ed12da8d</link><description>&lt;p&gt;上方 / 下方&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Summer lilac below a troubled sky." height="2000" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/z428/6a5a6ed12da8d.jpg" width="1126"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://z428.some.pics"&gt;@z428&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Jul 2026 18:05:07 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>苦乐循环</title><link>https://some.pics/6a59e655a00ba</link><description>&lt;p&gt;好时光与坏时光的循环。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Good-times-hard-times circle." height="720" referrerpolic